### OPT-004 : Range filters pour dates

**Règle** : Supporter start_date/end_date pour filtres temporels.

```python
# ✓ OPTIMAL
@router.get("")
async def list_entities(
    start_date: date | None = Query(None, description="Filter from date (YYYY-MM-DD)"),
    end_date: date | None = Query(None, description="Filter to date (YYYY-MM-DD)")
):
    filters = {}
    if start_date:
        filters["created_at__gte"] = datetime.combine(start_date, datetime.min.time())
    if end_date:
        filters["created_at__lte"] = datetime.combine(end_date, datetime.max.time())
    
    return await service.list(filters=filters)
```

